les/fundamental-rc/interval-merge-anim.mp4" type=3D"video/mp4" data-filtere=
d=3D"filtered"> Video tag is not supported.</video><i>Figure J: Green inter=
val should occlude red interval.</i></div><p>In <em>Figure J</em>, we can s=
ee that intervals earlier in the chain can <span class=3D"highlight">occlud=
e</span> intervals further down the chain.<br data-filtered=3D"filtered"> T=
o properly resolve this relation, we usually use a <span class=3D"highlight=
