filtered=3D"filtered"> This term is set during the <span class=3D"highlight=
">initial gathering</span>, it is <code>1.0</code> if the interval hit noth=
ing, and <code>0.0</code> if it did.</p><pre class=3D"language-glsl" data-l=
ang=3D"glsl" style=3D"color:#e8d4c0;background-color:#191919"><code class=
