e from the next cascade, we will get an obvious <span class=3D"highlight">g=
rid pattern</span>.</p><blockquote><p>The "next cascade" is the cascade abo=
ve the current one, it has lower spatial &amp; higher angular resolution.</=
p></blockquote><div class=3D"img"><img alt=3D"Figure L: Merging with neares=
