interval (in blue)." title=3D"Figure O: Merging for 1 interval (in blue)." =
src=3D"https://m4xc.dev/img/articles/fundamental-rc/full-merge.png" width=
=3D"360px"><i>Figure O: Merging for 1 interval (in blue).</i></div><p>Looki=
ng at <em>Figure O</em>, we get a visual of what those <span class=3D"highl=
