ith in cascade N+1 */
</span><span style=3D"color:#db784d">const </span><span style=3D"color:#95c=
c5e">ivec2</span><span> bilinear_texel </span><span style=3D"color:#db784d"=
>=3D</span><span> bilinear_index </span><span style=3D"color:#db784d">*</sp=
an><span> bilinear_size </span><span style=3D"color:#db784d">+</span><span>=
 bilinear_dir_coord;
</span></code></pre><p>Merging we do using the <code>merge_intervals</code>=
